title: 16-year-old shooting victim gets in car crash on the way to Valencia hospital
dc:creator: Alexandra E. Petri
description: A 16-year-old shot in Newhall was then transported in an auto that got in a single-car accident on the way to a hospital in Valencia.
content:encoded: A 16-year-old shot in Newhall was then transported in an auto that got in a single-car accident on the way to a hospital in Valencia.
